How to input values at runtime :- 
---------------------------------------------

   => To input values at runtime use variable prefixed with "&'.

          ex :-               a  :=  &a ; 

                            enter value for a :-  100

                                a  := 100;


                              a  :=  &x ; 

                            enter value for x :-  200

                            a := 200;

 
   DECLARE
         a   NUMBER(3);
         b   NUMBER(3);
         c   NUMBER(4);
   BEGIN
         a  := &a;
         b  := &b;
         c  :=  a+b;
         DBMS_OUTPUT.PUT_LINE(c);
   END;
      /
 
  enter value for a :- 200
  enter value for b :- 300

   o/p :- 500

